---
title: Speedy Beef, Spinach & Feta Rissoles with Greek Pita Salad
description: These simple rustic meatballs are packed with moisture and flavour from spinach and feta. They’re the perfect little parcels of joy to be savoured with a simple Greek pita salad and a herbed mayonnaise.
